category: Mail
requires: cygwin libesmtp5 openssl-devel
external-source: libesmtp
sdesc: "SMTP client library (development)"
ldesc: "libESMTP is an SMTP client which manages posting (or submission 
of) electronic mail via a preconfigured Mail Transport Agent (MTA). It 
may be used as part of a Mail User Agent (MUA) or other program that 
must be able to post electronic mail but where mail functionality is not 
that program's primary purpose."
